Package: fmpapi
Type: Package
Title: Flexible & Tidy Client for the Financial Modeling Prep API 
Version: 0.1.9.9001
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Christoph",
           family = "Scheuch",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           email = "christoph@tidy-intelligence.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-0423-6819"))
Description: A flexible and user-friendly interface to the Financial 
    Modeling Prep (FMP) API <https://site.financialmodelingprep.com/developer/docs>. 
    The package supports all available endpoints, making it easy to access financial 
    data such as stock prices, company metrics, and economic indicators. Returned data 
    is formatted in a tidy structure with snake_case column names.
